Package netistrar.clientapi.objects.domain

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DomainAvailability
    Domain availability class.
    DomainAvailabilityPrice
    Domain Availability Price objects are returned as part of the DomainAvailability object structure.
    DomainAvailabilityResults
    Encodes the results from a call to getHintedAvailability
    DomainNameContact
    An updatable contact object used within the Netistrar Domain Lifecycle API methods and as a related object to a DomainNameObject.
    DomainNameGlueRecord
    A value object used within the Domains API when listing or setting glue records for a domain name.
    DomainNameListResults
    A results object which wraps an array of DomainNameSummaryObject items returned from a call to listDomains within the Netistrar Domain Lifecycle API.
    DomainNameObject
    A value object used within the Netistrar Domain Lifecycle API methods to capture all of the properties of a domain name including related Contacts and Nameservers objects.
    DomainNameSummary
    Domain name summary object
    DomainNameTransferStatus
    This encodes details about a domain transfer.
